{"title":"书写在党的旗帜上","authors":["刘利华"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"书写在党的旗帜上（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘利华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔繁森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴礼帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高个子的孔繁森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向高原走去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荆棘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白发老母和妻拉长的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都没有将他留住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心系阿里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到哪儿背到哪儿的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只小药箱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装着百姓的疾苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风声和雨声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步步攀登"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人格巍峨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为人们心中的丰碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说青藏高原高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也与孔繁森齐肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔繁森摘下礼帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜马拉雅的海拔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李润五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是锻打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那把镰刀和斧头的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因而很硬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔掉输氧管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就去参加会议"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把生命的最后一次搏动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交给了会呼吸的党旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因心灵没有受潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铸铁打的李市长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才没有侵蚀生锈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩一叩李润五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铮铮作响"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}